<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reply Message</title>
</head>

<body style="font-family: 'Lucida Grande'; padding: 15px 8vw; color: #f5f5f5; background-color: #151515;">

    <div style="display: flex; justify-content: center; padding: 15px 0;">
        <img src="https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/sk-portfolio-website.appspot.com/o/portfolio-fevicon.png?alt=media&token=97dbef9b-1ba1-482d-97cb-8b4aa5dddecf"
            style="width: 65px;">
    </div>
    <h4>Hello <%= firstName lastName %>,
    </h4>
    <p>Thank You for posting message to me, here is the reply of your message</p>
    <p
        style="font-family: Verdana; margin: 25px 0; padding: 15px; font-size: small; color: rgb(15, 15, 15); background-color: white;">
        <%= message %>
    </p>

    <p>Thanks</p>
    <p>Sanket Talaviya</p>

    <p>
        PS: If you have further queries or discussions, feel free to contact through email or mobile</p>

</body>

</html>